{"tid":685904,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔BB入伙 求解答","createTime":"2018-05-31T21:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T01:43:08.000Z","uid":43738,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1201d527ddfd06dd93b8189898322494e99387","tid":685904,"uid":43738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T21:01:18.000Z","msg":"今日終於係朋友度帶左貓仔番屋企 <br />\n問左佢大約個半月多少少倒<br />\n問題係佢生活既地方本來好多虱 <br />\n己經係朋友度用左支frontline噴過同徙手捉左好多虱 <br />\n番到屋企再捉多輪仲係好多清唔曬 <br />\n想聽日帶佢去獸醫定邊度可以清左佢先 <br />\n上網又話無2個月又唔打得針又剩 <br />\n好想放佢出屋企走下玩下 佢叫到咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但太多虱真係搞唔掂 所以想快啲處理左先<br />\n有冇巴打比到建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/045954_02e265fbb1cec04eb1285c6ae5ef4531.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F045954_02e265fbb1cec04eb1285c6ae5ef4531.png&h=e3887e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫佢捉緊虱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/045955_02e265fbb1cec04eb1285c6ae5ef4531.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F045955_02e265fbb1cec04eb1285c6ae5ef4531.png&h=0b9fee9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f839be21cf13a2ef62553fcc0dcd3e3cda97c308","tid":685904,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:32:38.000Z","msg":"你滴完頭一劑 啲flee會慢慢死 再跌落地<br />\n基本上跌出黎個啲已經死左<br />\n你只需要當佢垃圾咁掃走<br />\n滴晒三劑先會完全清晒<br />\n當然啦 你可以帶去比獸醫睇睇"},{"pid":"0ad947b335657f90113f2bd4dcc4e15d00c629bd","tid":685904,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"唔係貓奴唔識答<br />\n但貓貓好得意<br />\n要養到佢肥肥白白哦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea3f3bf948630282ce861a7c4af8e951b3582e2","tid":685904,"